{"tid":574781,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺社會問題，係因為發展太急速","createTime":"2018-02-27T16:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T19:00:19.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1fbbbb8dadfb6ae4f4c44247b77e72f95a0769c4","tid":574781,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:37:17.000Z","msg":"好似教育咁<br />\n現在問題，唔係大學生太多<br />\n而係大學普及化太急太快<br />\n1990年2間，2000年變8間<br />\n短短10年暴增4倍<br />\n2016變10間<br />\n<br />\n2010至2015年大學大規模擴充發展，中大4間書院變9間書院，港大百週年校園，城大的大型新教學樓，浸大理大都起多幾座新教學樓。<br />\n<br />\n唔係太多大學生，而係一切來得太急，社會適應唔到。<br />\n<br />\n同埋教育時間太長，畢業已經22歲，社會係極度有需要將教學精簡濃縮，最好大部分人18歲前畢業，以免浪費學生生命。"},{"pid":"d9861010793d7342abc008ebb958d08d5aeb7b03","tid":574781,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"18歲前讀完大學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed84681db331217f2d42724a721d25ddce82786d","tid":574781,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"正常中學生18歲左右考dse"},{"pid":"0019e832b1148a8270e37b2478a9377b67078da0","tid":574781,"uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"係人口太多"},{"pid":"16c18235a0a189a7f71e12c43daad56e2bbba5e2","tid":574781,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"拆哂啲大學係咪就會冇哂社會問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efefa92bbb648e2dacf641116ec812fa9d19e4f3","tid":574781,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9861010793d7342abc008ebb958d08d5aeb7b03","tid":574781,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"18歲前讀完大學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"香港可以變菲律賓"},{"pid":"fb7265808af3da6ae28f8b6cf1c2a6c69561e810","tid":574781,"uid":82738,"lik